about.abouttext2: Cathedral Pines is a one of our Favorite locations that is  hidden in the Ponderosa Pine Trees of Black Forest. Close to North Colorado Springs. Most homes sit on 2.5 acre lots that are Custom Built by some of our favorite builders like Galiant Homes, All About Homes and Cooperleaf. There are hiking trails, ponds, views of the Front Range, water and community lodge for events. Give us a call if you like more information.
